---
 .../sqlite/patched/ext/fts3/fts3_tokenize_vtab.c    |  2 +-
 third_party/sqlite/patched/ext/fts3/fts3_write.c    |  2 +-
 third_party/sqlite/patched/test/fts3corrupt4.test   | 13 +++++++++++++
